msgctxt "sn35.84:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 35 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 35 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.84:0.2"
msgid "9. Channavagga "
msgstr "9. With Channa "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 84. Palokadhammasutta → paloka (pts1)
msgctxt "sn35.84:0.3"
msgid "84. Palokadhammasutta "
msgstr "84. Wearing Out "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn35.84:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.84:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā ānando yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami … pe … ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā ānando bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then Venerable Ānanda went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and said to him: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn35.84:2.1"
msgid "“‘Loko, loko’ti, bhante, vuccati. "
msgstr "“Sir, they speak of this thing called ‘the world’. "

msgctxt "sn35.84:2.2"
msgid "Kittāvatā nu kho, bhante, lokoti vuccatī”ti? "
msgstr "How is the world defined?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.84:2.3"
msgid "“Yaṃ kho, ānanda, palokadhammaṃ, ayaṃ vuccati ariyassa vinaye loko. "
msgstr "“Ānanda, that which wears out is called the world in the training of the noble one. "

msgctxt "sn35.84:2.4"
msgid "Kiñca, ānanda, palokadhammaṃ? "
msgstr "And what wears out? "

msgctxt "sn35.84:2.5"
msgid "Cakkhu kho, ānanda, palokadhammaṃ, rūpā palokadhammā, cakkhuviññāṇaṃ palokadhammaṃ, cakkhusamphasso palokadhammo, yampidaṃ cakkhusamphassapaccayā … pe … tampi palokadhammaṃ … pe … "
msgstr "The eye wears out. Sights … eye consciousness … eye contact wears out. The painful, pleasant, or neutral feeling that arises conditioned by eye contact also wears out. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.84:2.6"
msgid "jivhā palokadhammā, rasā palokadhammā, jivhāviññāṇaṃ palokadhammaṃ, jivhāsamphasso palokadhammo, yampidaṃ jivhāsamphassapaccayā … pe … tampi palokadhammaṃ … pe … "
msgstr "The ear … nose … tongue … body … "

msgctxt "sn35.84:2.7"
msgid "mano palokadhammo, dhammā palokadhammā, manoviññāṇaṃ palokadhammaṃ, manosamphasso palokadhammo, yampidaṃ manosamphassapaccayā uppajjati vedayitaṃ sukhaṃ vā dukkhaṃ vā adukkhamasukhaṃ vā tampi palokadhammaṃ. "
msgstr "The mind … thoughts … mind consciousness … mind contact wears out. The painful, pleasant, or neutral feeling that arises conditioned by mind contact also wears out. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.84:2.8"
msgid "Yaṃ kho, ānanda, palokadhammaṃ, ayaṃ vuccati ariyassa vinaye loko”ti. "
msgstr "That which wears out is called the world in the training of the noble one.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn35.84:2.9"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

